userInterface

Class LauncherUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • userInterface.LauncherUI

  • public class LauncherUI
extends javafx.application.Application
    This class is in charge of running all of the application level code. This includes sound processing, javafx stage work, Thread task managements, and all other levels of function. Imports for this class include java.sql classes, javafx concurrency classes, TarsosDSP library classes, javafx stage/scene controls, and the DBConnect and Sound classes from the client package.
    Version:
    1.3.4
    Author:
    Jonathan Novins
